<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:21.3pt; text-align:justify; line-height:normal; font-size:12.5pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Мазкур сана байрам ёки дам олиш кунига тўғри келган ҳолларда кейинги иш куни тўловларни амалга оширишнинг охирги куни хисобланади.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:21.3pt; text-align:justify; line-height:normal; font-size:12.5pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">2.5.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Улушдорга мулк ҳуқуқи билан топшириладиган объектдаги ишлар таркиби ва ҳажми қуйидаги шартларни ҳисобга олган ҳолда, архитектура-дизайн фирмаси томонидан ишлаб чиқилган лойиҳага мос келиши керак:</span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:21.3pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:normal; font-size:12.5pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">1)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Хонадон</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">ичидаги</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">қурилиш</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">ишлари: тўлиқ битган</span><br><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">2)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Электр</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">таъминотига</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">оид</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">ишлар: электрлашган&nbsp;</span><br><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">3)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Табиий</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">газ</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">таъминотига</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">оид</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">ишлар: газлашган</span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:21.3pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:normal; font-size:12.5pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">4)</span><span style="font-size:11pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Иситиш мосламалари урнатилган (котёл, радиатор)</span><br><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">5)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Сантехника</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">ишлари: тўлиқ бажарилган</span><br><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">6)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Телефон,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">интернетга</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">оид</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">ишлар: интернетлашган</span><br><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">7)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Уйни</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">пардозлаш</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">ишлари: тўлиқ бажарилган</span><br><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">8)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Бошқа</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; background-color:#ffffff;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">ишлар: келишилмаган.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:21.3pt; text-align:justify; line-height:normal; font-size:12.5pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Томонлар лойиҳада кўрсатилмаган ишлар таркиби ва ҳажми, фойдаланиладиган маҳсулотлар, ўрнатиладиган мосламалар, воситалар ва жиҳозлар тури Қурувчи томонидан мустақил ҳал этилишига келишиб олдилар.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:21.3pt; text-align:justify; line-height:normal; font-size:12.5pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">2.6.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">Қурилиш объектининг тугалланиши ва Улушдорга топшириш муддати&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">2025 йил&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">III</span></strong><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">(учинчи) чорак</span></strong><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;деб белгиланган. Қуйидаги ҳолатлар бундан мустасно:&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:21.3pt; text-align:justify; line-height:normal; font-size:12.5pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">қурилиш объектини тугалланиш муддатига енгиб бўлмайдиган куч (форс-мажор) холатлари сабаб бўлса;</span></p>
<p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:21.3pt; line-height:normal; font-size:12.5pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';">қурилиш ишлари хажми буюртмачи томонидан ўзгартирилса.</span></p>
